{"tid":2448176,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有5個月，工人姐姐就走了..","createTime":"2021-03-15T17:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T07:56:00.000Z","uid":138802,"like":184,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1938c2de6661cefce2686f5cc42637986cea717c","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"一齊住咗十幾年嘅工人姐姐要番鄉下嫁人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2447681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2447681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢個po，原本想留言，但越打越多野講，所以決定自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為喊緊，所以會打到1999，辛苦晒你地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有一個工人姐姐，佢係我出世前三日已經黎到我屋企，到宜家21年了<br />\n<br />\n屋企呀爸呀媽家姐都要番工，所以相處得最多就係工人姐姐，好多時屋企都淨係得我地兩個，我份人好怕醜又少野講，我淨係對住佢先可以暢所欲言<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個比家姐恰，佢會幫我同媽咪講，幫我出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學打交，然後可能比學校記過，我好驚比呀媽知，我同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學同老師講大話，又係好驚，又係淨係敢同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考dse果陣好大壓力，又淨係會同佢講，佢又會好好咁幫我揼骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識到女朋友，又係第一個同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，帶佢番屋企佢又好識做唔會同呀媽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好記得佢講番，細個呀媽問我錫邊個多d，我話係工人姐姐<br />\n同埋佢以前星期日出去放假，我會隔住個鐵閘咁喊住叫佢番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話佢每次都好唔捨得我，搞到佢都想喊，自此佢每次朝早就會盡量唔嘈醒我，廢事見到我喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前年套淪落人，我知道自己一定會喊到七彩，我就自己一個去睇，結果喊到眼都痛，要係商場等到好番d先走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71a801a2079ca88149f5764bb816aef8e5e5a10","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":175,"dislike":3,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"其實上年已經決定左，佢8月就會走，我一路都冇乜野，可能係逃避，但直到今日睇到個po真係情緒大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同屋企諗住等佢同我慶祝埋我8月生日，佢就會走<br />\n我呢幾年都一路幻想究竟果日會係點<br />\n我覺得我會冇勇氣送佢去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚我唔比佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做唔出笑住咁送佢走..<br />\n<br />\n我講野唔叻，又唔識講呢d肉麻野，加上大個左成日打機/入房，已經好少同佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但要我諗樣野同佢傾計又諗唔到..<br />\n<br />\n我嘅童年回憶入面，有好多開心或者難忘嘅時刻都係有佢份，佢經歷過晒我由小學到中學再到大學嘅轉變，幾個月後大學畢業就係呢個旅程嘅終點..真係好難想像屋企冇左佢會係點..<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話第時我結婚要同佢講，佢可能會飛番黎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀爸會整一塊牌送比佢，佢叫我諗一句野寫落去，我都未諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗住再送份好d嘅禮物比佢<br />\n<br />\n佢係我生命中好重要嘅人，咁樣一走真係冇咩可能會再見，我係好著重感情，由其係親情嘅人，佢走=親人死左一樣..真係唔識點面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢d冇得用一言兩語講晒出黎，我都唔可以趁一個po表達晒出黎，但我真係好想好想抒發晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b4ad751edf6cff431ed2d02bbf2b6126bdb7f","tid":2448176,"uid":9193,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"唔好唔開心 <br />\n既然你都當佢係屋企人<br />\n祝佢一路順風 永遠幸福啦<br />\n第時咪去果邊旅行搵佢玩囉"},{"pid":"04a69d7c550859a321388b98a39be1da4e4520e1","tid":2448176,"uid":38904,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"其實你覺得咁重要點解你唔留佢contact?<br />\n遲啲開返關可以當探個朋友啊"},{"pid":"ea416cec8c4787d446251e59caa67ec352a6c227","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f63b4ad751edf6cff431ed2d02bbf2b6126bdb7f","tid":2448176,"uid":9193,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"唔好唔開心 <br />\n既然你都當佢係屋企人<br />\n祝佢一路順風 永遠幸福啦<br />\n第時咪去果邊旅行搵佢玩囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"咁當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住第時大個事業有成<br />\n會著晒西裝飛過去搵佢<br />\n但驚去到見到就會唔捨得走..唉"},{"pid":"620d04de17de27e6f9a37bfb538e94547c45f42d","tid":2448176,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"我以前請過四個工人<br />\n依家都keep住有聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b2c9be5c7594b5ccc44fb976960f379d0fab21","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"樓主喊到碌柒咁  face id都認唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n密碼又入極唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要好番d先開到signal"},{"pid":"5c9f17b6284d5f9551c372bf6dac060b048bd94d","tid":2448176,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"620d04de17de27e6f9a37bfb538e94547c45f42d","tid":2448176,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"我以前請過四個工人<br />\n依家都keep住有聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"生左仔女又wts share 俾我地"},{"pid":"b2742e747b77c3fc635ae07d69c43284cb6c279a","tid":2448176,"uid":97010,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"21年同住， 親過絕大部份親人添啦"},{"pid":"edfd702a4b7c9735b3d1e09803da1cbad84dfe0a","tid":2448176,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲嫁人？"},{"pid":"121725760f741d2569724d1db3e4f5e81bf129db","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a69d7c550859a321388b98a39be1da4e4520e1","tid":2448176,"uid":38904,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"其實你覺得咁重要點解你唔留佢contact?<br />\n遲啲開返關可以當探個朋友啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"本身諗住遲d先...一路都唔想諗呢件事<br />\n但我有佢fb了，我諗有呢個可以拎埋佢印尼電話、地址之類"},{"pid":"3849543677b6a83f2565f5f272b5c54ddd9deb78","tid":2448176,"uid":198992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 出世睇到我十八歲 都係走之前五個月喊到痴線 dse都冇心情考 <br />\n仲記得上年喺飛機睇倫落人睇到喊左好多次"},{"pid":"279aad114b75d0bf797c59d8e493295e75720577","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"620d04de17de27e6f9a37bfb538e94547c45f42d","tid":2448176,"uid":108794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"我以前請過四個工人<br />\n依家都keep住有聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:59:20.000Z","msg":"四個唔及一個由頭到尾感情深<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋工人呢個定位好特別，冇血緣關係，但係會由細睇到自己大，去到某個位就會離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇工人真係好難明呢個感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58d045447b2004935ff56f9d30ac3c3288d3465","tid":2448176,"uid":260008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以前工人又係由細睇到我大，佢返去我都好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都叫有保持聯絡，知佢生活得開心就夠了"},{"pid":"3ee66e0c4788920a603e35a2ca1050e300d85683","tid":2448176,"uid":358288,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港好多小朋友都有工人姐姐親過自己父母嘅感覺，見過好多小朋友唔開心或者放學都係衝去攬住工人姐姐、而唔係佢老母。但工人姐姐唔會陪一世，好似樓主咁大個先要分離真係好殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n長年離家，工人姐姐同樓主可能親過同佢自己仔女，咁樣又係sad 。<br />\n<br />\n父母陪小朋友嘅時間真係緊要過個幾皮嘢一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲奴隸制度唔應該繼續落去，搞到兩個家庭嘅小朋友都sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4821a0268683cccd9a80a1cc601006e58e2e99a","tid":2448176,"uid":138802,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"edfd702a4b7c9735b3d1e09803da1cbad84dfe0a","tid":2448176,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲嫁人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:46:50.000Z","msg":"佢係結左婚先黎香港架<br />\n我仲以為全部工人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽佢講  佢老公直情帶女人番屋企，佢寄番去d錢又比佢拎去亂用<br />\n呢d廢男人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9873a13d037b754f0b096cf6e2281b53f0ed1f","tid":2448176,"uid":358288,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:49:37.000Z","msg":"不過樓主要勇敢d面對，同埋呢幾個月調整下心態去接受。<br />\n<br />\n信我，一定要送佢機。<br />\n<br />\n連你咁親都唔送佢機佢會好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e47ca641ba2b6500cd226dd1e3227f1d7840dd","tid":2448176,"uid":88214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"好在資訊科技發達咗，有心聯繫實得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋咁多年相處，唔會斬得甩嘅"},{"pid":"8e2e0e770eadc13740cbf98f893f37f9fb817f0b","tid":2448176,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T18:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"